#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn45.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.10:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Avijjāvagga "
msgstr "1. Ignorance "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Nandiyasutta "
msgstr "10. With Nandiya "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.10:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.10:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho nandiyo paribbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then the wanderer Nandiya went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "sn45.10:1.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho nandiyo paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side, and said to the Buddha: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.10:1.4"
msgid "“kati nu kho, bho gotama, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nibbānaṅgamā honti nibbānaparāyanā nibbānapariyosānā”ti? "
msgstr "“Master Gotama, how many things, when developed and cultivated, have extinguishment as their culmination, destination, and end?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.12, sc2
msgctxt "sn45.10:2.1"
msgid "“Aṭṭhime kho, nandiya, dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nibbānaṅgamā honti nibbānaparāyanā nibbānapariyosānā. "
msgstr "“These eight things, when developed and cultivated, have extinguishment as their culmination, destination, and end. "

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.2"
msgid "Katame aṭṭha? "
msgstr "What eight? "

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.3"
msgid "Seyyathidaṃ—sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. "
msgstr "They are: right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, nandiya, aṭṭha dhammā bhāvitā bahulīkatā nibbānaṅgamā honti nibbānaparāyanā nibbānapariyosānā”ti. "
msgstr "These eight things, when developed and cultivated, have extinguishment as their culmination, destination, and end.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.10:2.5"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, nandiyo paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, the wanderer Nandiya said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.6"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! … "

msgctxt "sn45.10:2.7"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.10:2.8"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.10:2.9"
msgid "Avijjāvaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn45.10:3.1"
msgid "Avijjañca upaḍḍhañca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.10:3.2"
msgid "sāriputto ca brāhmaṇo; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.10:3.3"
msgid "Kimatthiyo ca dve bhikkhū, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn45.10:3.4"
msgid "vibhaṅgo sūkanandiyāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
